title: Snowpark 1.15.0  - com.snowflake.snowpark.GetResult
paragraphs: This package contains all Snowpark logical types.
This package contains all Snowpark logical types.
Represents the results of downloading a file from a stage location to the local file system.

NOTE:
         
          fileName
         
         is the relative path to the file on the stage. For example, if you
      download
         
          @myStage/prefix1/file1.csv.gz
         
         ,
         
          fileName
         
         is
         
          prefix1/file1.csv.gz
         
         .
